This Terms and Conditions Agreement (the “Agreement”) is a legal agreement between you (“Trainer”, “you”, or “your”) and DaDaGym Fitness Center (“DaDaGym”, “we”, “us”, or “our”) for your use of the DaDaGym trainer platform and services.

1. GENERAL TERMS
1.1 Acceptance
By registering as a trainer, you agree to be bound by this Agreement.

1.2 Services
DaDaGym provides a platform to connect trainers with members. Trainers deliver services at DaDaGym facilities.

2. TRAINER ELIGIBILITY AND RESPONSIBILITIES
2.1 Qualifications
You represent you hold valid certifications (e.g., NASM, ACE), CPR/AED training, and 2+ years experience. Provide proof upon request.

2.2 Conduct
- Arrive 10 minutes early.
- Professional attire.
- Maintain client confidentiality.
- No photos/videos without written consent.
- Report injuries/equipment issues immediately.

2.3 Prohibited Conduct
- Harassment or discrimination.
- Solicitation outside platform.
- Use of banned substances.
- Violation leads to immediate termination.

3. LIABILITY AND INSURANCE
3.1 Trainer Insurance
You must maintain $1,000,000 general liability insurance naming DaDaGym as additional insured.

3.2 Indemnification
You agree to indemnify and hold DaDaGym harmless from claims arising from your negligence.

3.3 No DaDaGym Liability
DaDaGym not liable for your actions, client injuries, or equipment use.

4. PAYMENTS
4.1 Commission
70% to trainer, 30% to DaDaGym, paid weekly via direct deposit.

4.2 Taxes
You responsible for all taxes.

5. TERMINATION
5.1 By DaDaGym
Immediate for breach, complaints, certification lapse.

5.2 By Trainer
30 days written notice.

6. CONFIDENTIALITY
Protect member data (health, contact). Breach subjects to legal action.

7. GOVERNING LAW
Subject to laws of [State/Country].

